Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.35,0:22:10.14,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,I decided to be stronger than anyone around
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.14,0:22:13.40,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,Goodbye old self goodbye
